{
  "texts": [
    "\"As an average UK resident I see a moderate social value in the occupation of a Chatbot Conversation Trainer.",
    "I understand that in today's digital age, machine learning and AI are increasingly becoming a part of our daily lives, and chatbots are commonly used in customer service and information provision sectors.",
    "Therefore, people who can train these chatbots to interact effectively and humanely with users are important.",
    "However, I also acknowledge that this job may not have a direct interaction or contribution to the community or societal well-being in the same way as occupations in health care, education or social services would, hence the slightly above mid-range score.",
    "It might also not be intuitively understood or valued particularly highly by certain segments of the population, particularly older demographics or people in areas with less access to or engagement with technology.\""
  ]
}